            <title>[PDFBOX-2266] NPE when converting page to image</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2266</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have a pdf that throws an NPE in version 2.0.0 when rendering a specific page to an image.  I&apos;ve tested the pdf with 1.8.6 and it worked correctly.  It logged a warning (java.io.IOException: Error: Unknown shading type 0) but did not throw any exceptions.  I will attach the pdf.  Let me know if you need any more info.&lt;/p&gt;

